                "Nutanix AHV regressions mostly resolved"
            ],
            "severity": "MEDIUM"
        },
        "9.5.0": {
            "known_issues": [
                "Azure SSD v2 disk type required for cloud clusters",
                "S3 Glacier Deep Archive integration changes"
            ],
